data.description:
Updated price point giving you even more equity on day one. 
YES!! Beautiful ranch with open floor plan. 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car, home on a full basement.  Walk into your large living room with fireplace and built in storage. As you pass thru the dinning/kitchen area (check out the beautiful butcher block counter tops) - you can walk out onto the back porch or head into the master bedroom suite. This home offers a divided bedroom floor plan for added privacy. Down the hall brings you to the other two bedroom and your main floor laundry before entering the 2 car garage. This home has so much to offer from a prime location to the full basement with 9' ceilings just waiting on your finishing touches. Come see for yourself.
